{
  "url": "https://qsimulate.com/products/quantumfp",
  "markdown": "[![](https://qsimulate.com/images/nav-bar/logo-dark.svg)](https://qsimulate.com/home)\n  * [Home](https://qsimulate.com/home)\n  * [Products](https://qsimulate.com/products)\n  * [Technology](https://qsimulate.com/technology)\n  * [About Us](https://qsimulate.com/about-us)\n  * [News](https://qsimulate.com/news)\n  * [Careers](https://qsimulate.com/careers)\n  * [Other](https://qsimulate.com/other)\n  * [Get in Touch ![](https://qsimulate.com/images/home/learn-arrow.svg)](https://qsimulate.com/#info)\n\u00a92022 QSimulate, All rights reserved.\n\n\nBy using qsimulate.com, you agree to the use of cookies and our[cookie policy](https://qsimulate.com/cookies).\nOK\n# QuantumFP\n### Accelerating AI Drug Discovery with Quantum Fingerprinting.\n## QuantumFP: Quantum Mechanical 3D Fingerprinting\nQuantum mechanics can readily evaluate the effects of covalent bond formation utilizing automated approaches that can be integrated into dock scoring, AI/ML workflows, and applied toward goals such as warhead tuning. Transform 2D representations to 3D structures with ease, and generate quantum mechanical data for large machine learning models through our automated workflow. Feed ML models a higher volume of data with quantum accuracy!\n## QuantumFP Features\n## Accurate\nWhen it comes to accuracy, quantum-driven 3D characterization is the way to go. Quantum mechanics has proven to be more reliable in identifying correct low-energy conformers and provides a wider array of descriptors that molecular mechanics simply can't touch.\n## Fast\nWith just one click, generate 3D structures for millions of compounds. What's more? The quantum mechanical properties are included in the output for each one.\n## Affordable\nBudget-savvy? We've got you covered. QSimulate\u2019s software platform is optimized for less expensive 'spot instance' computing. Calculate vast quantities of data for significantly less than wet lab experiments.\n![](https://qsimulate.com/images/product/QuantumFP-AI-Icon.png)\n## QuantumFP by the numbers  \n| Throughput  |  **> 30,000,000** conformers per day  |  \n| --- | --- |  \n| Computing cost  |  **$15 per 30,000 conformers** (1K molecule, 30 conf each)  |  \n| Success rate  |  **> 99.9994%** (measured on ~1,000,000 molecules)  |  \n![logo dark](https://qsimulate.com/images/nav-bar/logo-dark.svg)\n## QuantumFP\n### Accelerating Drug Discovery with Quantum Fingerprinting\n## Additional Content\n[Download Whitepaper](https://kb.qsimulate.com/quantumfp)\n[View Webinar](https://kb.qsimulate.com/high-throughput-quantum-mechanics-based-3d-molecular-fingerprinting)\n[Schedule a Meeting](https://kb.qsimulate.com/schedule-a-meeting)\n[![](https://qsimulate.com/images/product/LinkedIn_icon.svg)](https://www.linkedin.com/company/qsimulate)[![](https://qsimulate.com/images/product/youtube.png)](https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCefPnTnV_AsuLtkSyCwaTBg)![](https://qsimulate.com/images/nav-bar/email.svg)\n  * ![](https://qsimulate.com/images/nav-bar/logo-light.svg)\n  * \u00a92022 QSimulate, All rights reserved.\n\n\n  * Get In Touch\n  * ![](https://qsimulate.com/images/nav-bar/email.svg)info@qsimulate.com\n  * ![](https://qsimulate.com/images/nav-bar/phone.svg)+1-(617)249-4828\n  * 20 Guest St, STE 101, Boston, MA 02135, USA\n  * [![](https://qsimulate.com/images/about/team-linkedin-gray.svg)LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/company/qsimulate/)\n\n\n  * Site Map\n  * [Home](https://qsimulate.com/home)\n  * [Products](https://qsimulate.com/products)\n  * [Technology](https://qsimulate.com/technology)\n  * [About Us](https://qsimulate.com/about-us)\n  * [News](https://qsimulate.com/news)\n  * [Careers](https://qsimulate.com/careers)\n  * [Other](https://qsimulate.com/other)\n\n\n  * User Policies\n  * [Terms & Conditions](https://qsimulate.com/terms)\n  * [Privacy Policy](https://qsimulate.com/privacy)\n  * [Cookie Policy](https://qsimulate.com/cookies)\n  * [FCOI Policy](https://qsimulate.com/files/policies/fcoi_policy.pdf)\n\n